---

# Backend Modules

## fingerprint.py

Contains:

* pHash similarity
* ORB matching
* Histogram similarity
* Combined scoring

---

## watermark.py

Contains:

* Watermark embedding
* Watermark extraction
* Watermark verification

---

## matcher.py

Decision engine:

Flow:

```text
Check watermark first
If found:
  Watermark Verified
Else:
  Run fingerprint similarity
```

---

## alerts.py

Generates:

* High severity alerts
* Medium review alerts
* Authorized usage pass-through

---

## scanner.py

Simulates monitored external content feed.

---

# API Endpoints

## Register Asset

```http
POST /register-asset
```

Registers media and embeds watermark.

---

## Check Originality

```http
POST /check-originality
```

Checks suspicious media.

Possible outputs:

Watermark route:

```json
{
 "status":"Watermark Verified",
 "ownership":"Confirmed"
}
```

Fingerprint route:

```json
{
 "combined":62.98,
 "status":"Needs Review"
}
```

---

## Monitoring Scan

```http
GET /run-scan
```

Returns simulated alerts.

---

## Health Check

```http
GET /
```

Returns:

```json
{
 "status":"API Running"
}
```

